  "title": "🚑 Paramedic (EMS – PRM) | Up to $3,700 + Allowances + Bonuses",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚑 Paramedic (EMS – PRM) | Up to $3,700 + Allowances +\nBonuses</strong></p><p>Location: Islandwide </p><p>Work Type: Full-time | Shift-based</p><p>Salary Range: Up to $3,700 + Allowances + Bonuses</p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>Step into a leadership role as a Paramedic and Crew Leader responding to emergency calls, ensuring timely and high-quality pre-hospital care.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the EMS crew during emergency responses</li><li>Provide advanced pre-hospital care and patient stabilization</li><li>Manage crew operations, including ambulance readiness and equipment checks</li><li>Ensure compliance with operational and administrative KPIs</li><li>Mentor and guide junior EMTs/EMTDs during shifts</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>✅Paramedic Course recognized by the Ministry of Health (MOH)</p><p>✅ Operationally ready and physically fit for emergency response</p><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li>Lead EMS frontline crews and make a real impact saving lives</li><li>Gain exclusive operational training not accessible outside</li><li>Competitive salary, allowances, and bonuses</li><li>Flexible shift patterns promoting better work-life control</li><li>Structured career progression with educational sponsorships</li></ul><p><strong>Ready to Save Lives and Serve with Pride?</strong></p><p>Apply now and take the first step toward an exciting EMS career with real impact.</p><p>Send your resume in MS Word format to:\n<strong>Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</strong></p><p>Please include your <strong>availability, notice period, and expected salary.</strong></p><p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>E.A. 24C2435</p>",
